<doc>
  <member name="D3D12_SHADER_BYTECODE">
    <summary>
      <para>Describes shader data.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>The <see cref="D3D12_GRAPHICS_PIPELINE_STATE_DESC" /> and <see cref="D3D12_COMPUTE_PIPELINE_STATE_DESC" /> objects contain <b>D3D12_SHADER_BYTECODE</b> structures that describe various shader types.</para>
      <para>When loading a shader from FXC/DXC, this may be the entire compiled blob as is loaded from disk.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/commandlistcast">CD3DX12_SHADER_BYTECODE</seealso>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/direct3d-12-structures">Core Structures</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_SHADER_BYTECODE.pShaderBytecode">
    <summary>
      <para>A pointer to a memory block that contains the shader data.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_SHADER_BYTECODE.BytecodeLength">
    <summary>
      <para>The size, in bytes, of the shader data that the <b>pShaderBytecode</b> member points to.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>